name: Custom Facebook Christmas Greeting
description:
Save money this year by sending your Christmas greetings through Facebook! We'll create a graphic with photos of your family OR we'll get one of our sheepdogs to draw em!

Price will be determined after we learn more about your project. Please contact us at aaron@sheepdoggreetings.com to get your Facebook greeting started!

name: Custom Christmas Postcard
description:
Why spend more than you have to on Christmas cards? A postcard is a great way to send your greetings, have it look great and save money!

We will design your greeting using 4 photos of your choosing and put it in the following template. All we need from you is the photos!

Contact us at aaron@sheepdoggreetings.com with any questions and to get your order started today! Allow 10-14 days for delivery and production. Printing/pricing will be determined upon order size.

name: Custom Greeting Card
description:
Great for weddings, Christmas, birthday, etc! Cost depends on complexity of card, but generally runs between $150-$200. Cost does not include printing. Size of card/postcard varies. 

Email aaron@sheepdoggreetings.com for specific pricing and details. Allow 2-3 weeks for turn-around.

name: Custom Photo Calendar
description:
Customize your very own calendar with photos from the past year. As shown, your photos will look great in this CD jewel case. Price includes 12 photos of your choosing for each month, printing and shipping.

Get one for you, a family member, friend or for your company! Turn-around is typically 1-2 weeks from purchase.

Contact us for more details: aaron@sheepdoggreetings.com.
